summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to the Water Department; authorizing revision of an existing contract with C. A. Harris & Son, Inc. and Chelan Box & Mfg. Co., Inc., Washington corporations, for the purchase of certain land in Chelan County, Washington, to be utilized by way of an intermediate exchange with the State of Washington, Department of Game, to acquire Forest Service property in the Cedar River Watershed; and partially superseding Ordinance 99760.
